                    <span>This book is phenomenal and the best I have read on the subject.  Very few people have the experience Tim does, as both a psychologist and successful businessman, so he has great credibility.  His system/process makes dealing with conflict a breeze.  And I love his humor.  I feel connected with him and trust his advice.  I highly recommend this book!<p>Michael Charest <br>Speaker, Coach<br>BUSINESS GROWTH SOLUTIONS<br>and<br>COACH & GROW R.I.C.H.<br>(...)<br>"Grow your business, grow your life!"<br>(...)</span>
                  
